@gordongram is the man! Love his PUB @caesarspalace 
This place is a top flight restaurant without being too expensive. The #chickenwings are some of the best ever. Subtle heat, not too acidic and not too salty. Crispy yet tender and moist. Saucy yet not too messy. Such a well rounded flavor profile. Not the lazy typical vinegar bomb #Hotsauce Perfect sides of celery, carrots and blue cheese dressing. With extra blue crumble on the side. This place rocks. Service, comfort, decor, food, drink, value, all come in with honors. Plus a nice #HappyHour I'll be back for more.
#foodsnob
